			<CASNumber>12125-02-9</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Ammonium chloride is an inorganic compound used in various applications such as fertilizers, metallurgy, pharmaceuticals, and in the food industry. It is a crystalline salt that is highly soluble in water and oftentimes appears in white powder form. In the production process, it is commonly obtained as a by-product of the Solvay process for sodium carbonate synthesis, or directly from ammonia and hydrogen chloride. Ammonium chloride adheres to relevant quality and safety standards for its respective applications. It is commonly available to consumers in packaged form or to industries in bulk 'at plant'.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氯化铵是一种无机化合物，在肥料、冶金、制药和食品工业等多种应用中使用。它是一种高度溶于水的白色粉末状结晶盐，在生产过程中通常是作为索尔维过程中合成碳酸钠的副产品获得，或者直接从氨和氯化氢反应中获得。氯化铵遵循其相应应用的相关质量和安全标准。它通常以包装形式面向消费者或以批量形式在工厂供应。</common:generalComment>
